ENTRY_END

STEP 21 CHECK_ANSWER
ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH all
REPLY QR AA RD RA NOERROR
SECTION QUESTION
refused.trigger.check.max.number.of.upstream.queries. IN TXT
SECTION ANSWER
